175
00:21:10,685 --> 00:21:13,207
Wood run away with rope-walks of line.

176
00:21:14,008 --> 00:21:15,229
Prodigies are told of him.

177
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:17,351
Adieu, sulphur-bottom.

178
00:21:17,591 --> 00:21:21,355
I can say nothing more that is true of ye, nor can the oldest Nantucketer.

179
